node.text: This is the brand new Ferrari 812 Competizione and a very first look to check it out! Join me at Fiorano, Ferrari's test track in Maranello, Italy, to walk around the new limited edition super-GT and go through all of the details. #Ferrari #812Competizione #812 #Shmee150

node.title: Check Out the New FERRARI 812 COMPETIZIONE! First Look

node.text: The gullwing doors on the SLS AMG (and in this case the epic Black Series) aren't just for show, they also do a pretty good job of access when space is tight. Here's a perfect example next to my Supra of how little space you need, which you might well find surprising! #Mercedes #SLSAMG #BlackSeries #Gullwing #Shmee150

node.title: SLS AMG Gullwing Doors are Winning!

node.text: The GT8 Club head to the Aston Martin factory for a meet up and that means we can also check out the spec room for the new Valkyrie hypercar!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Tim - Shmee on July 29, 2021 tagging @mercedesbenz, @mercedesamg, @shmee150wastaken, @theshmeemobiles, and @theshmuseum. May be an image of 1 person and car.

node.text: It's time, I'm selling @theshmeemobiles AMG GT R Pro. It's an awesome car and so much of me would like to keep it in the collection as the purest AMG GT model, and probably even rarer than the Black Series! However, with the GT Black Series, and now the C63 Black Series in the garage it's a hard one to justify and as such it'll move on. Before that though, taking it out for a last drive! #Mercedes #AMG #AMGGTR #GTRPro #Shmeemobile #Shmee150

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Tim - Shmee on July 27, 2021 tagging @mercedesamg, @exclusiveautos_, @shmee150wastaken, and @theshmeemobiles. May be an image of car.

node.text: I think you could see this one coming to @theshmeemobiles! Collecting at @exclusiveautos_, a @mercedesamg C63 Black Series joins the garage to complete my dream trio of the Black Series models. The collection video is live now, heading over with the GT BS and G63 to bring the car back home that I've been planning for a while since driving my friend @gercollector's car last summer. It's a noisy, shouty thing, just perfect with the M156 6.2l V8! #Mercedes #AMG #C63BlackSeries #BlackSeries #Shmeemobile #Shmee150

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Tim - Shmee on July 27, 2021 tagging @shmee150wastaken, @theshmeemobiles, and @theshmuseum. May be an image of 1 person and car.

node.text: I might have lost my marbles, another AMG is joining @theshmeemobiles today! We're taking out the GT Black Series and G63 for a run to @exclusiveautos_ to pick up something I've been keen to add to the collection for a while, and is very on theme... What do you think it's going to be? #Mercedes #AMG #GTBlackSeries #G63 #Shmeemobile #Shmee150

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Tim - Shmee on July 26, 2021 tagging @jonnycarpervert, @shmee150wastaken, @theshmeemobiles, and @theshmuseum. May be an image of 2 people and car.

node.text: The one and only @jonnycarpervert came to visit @theshmuseum with his tatty old chairs! Great to shoot for @thelatebrakeshow and catch up after a while. Fun fact, we filmed a car spotting segment for Fifth Gear together back in 2013! #LateBrakeShow #TheShmuseum #Shmee150

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Tim - Shmee on July 25, 2021 tagging @mercedesamg, @shmee150wastaken, @avantgarde_mb, and @theshmeemobiles. May be an image of 1 person and car.

node.text: It's been a long time since we've seen @theshmeemobiles SLS Black Series, in fact I hadn't even laid eyes on it once this calendar year until my visit to @avantgarde_mb to update you on it now. Long story short, after the audio installation, while I was away still in the USA, some parts failed that were on huge back order and it's taken about 4 months to source them with the global parts supply issues at the moment. The good news is that it just needs to be put back together now and it can finally join the rest of the collection at @theshmuseum at long last. For now though, a great opportunity for the new GT Black Series to get 300 running in miles down, and the two together for the first time #Mercedes #AMG #SLSAMG #BlackSeries #SLSBlackSeries #Shmeemobile #Shmee150

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Tim - Shmee on July 24, 2021 tagging @ferrari, @shmee150wastaken, and @ferrariuk. May be an image of 1 person and car.

node.text: Been to test drive the new @ferrari Portofino M! It's an appropriate refresh for the model, with the new 8 speed gearbox, more power, and it sounds surprisingly impressive too. I've always thought that the Portofino is a great looking car, and gets unfairly given a reputation as the entry Ferrari, but few other cars in the segment would be able to offer as much as this does #Ferrari #PortofinoM #testdrive #Shmee150

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Tim - Shmee on July 22, 2021 tagging @astonmartinlagonda, @shmee150wastaken, @theshmeemobiles, and @theshmuseum. May be an image of 1 person, car and text that says 'V3RKD'.

node.text: I bought it back! The missing member of @theshmeemobiles has returned home, my former Aston Martin V8 Vantage Roadster is here at @theshmuseum and back in my collection after 9 years. This was the first car to ever be called 'The Shmeemobile' and my first ever video talking to camera was while driving it, not to mention the first road trip vlogs I ever uploaded. It was really the start of everything with a very special place in my heart, so to have it back is a dream. Thankfully, it doesn't disappoint in the slightest, and it's amazing to see how well it has kept up despite being 12 years old. In fact it had 19k miles when I sold it, and only 12k more through to today, so still very much feels like my car! #AstonMartin #V8Vantage #VantageRoadster #Shmeemobile #TheShmuseum #Shmee150

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Tim - Shmee on July 21, 2021 tagging @astonmartinlagonda, and @shmee150wastaken. May be an image of 1 person, car and outdoors.

node.text: The all carbon @astonmartinlagonda Valkyrie is not only stunning but a truly ferocious experience. I can confirm from riding onboard this rocketship (it's no ordinary 'car'), that this is really a different beast. I've never felt anything that can wear number plates like it, and I'm not sure anything else ever will be capable of the same. A few laps with @darrenturner007 told me everything I need to know, and it's far from sanity; performance without compromise, just don't expect to have much space to move inside! #AstonMartin #Valkyrie #Shmee150

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Tim - Shmee on July 18, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and car.

node.text: Welcome to @theshmeemobiles, my @mercedesamg GT Black Series! The journey is only just beginning with collection from @mercedesbenz_retailgroup in Graphite Grey Magno, a true Batmobile if ever there was one, but believe me when I say there's a lot to come. From how much I enjoy my SLS Black Series, and the various AMG GT Rs that I've owned, I cannot wait to get this car out and about. As I've said, it is going to change to AMG Solarbeam yellow, it's going to be going ASAP to the @nuerburgring and a visit to @opus_innovation but first, back to @theshmuseum! #Mercedes #AMG #GTBlackSeries #Shmeemobile #collectionday #Shmee150

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Tim - Shmee on July 18, 2021 tagging @mercedesamg, @mercedesbenz_retailgroup, and @shmee150wastaken. May be an image of 1 person and indoor.

node.text: It's a @mercedesamg kind of day! The new addition to @theshmeemobiles has arrived at long last and today is the day to reveal it, then bring it to @theshmuseum to join the collection! My love for the GT platform is no secret, having owned a number of them in recent years, but this is the ultimate incarnation and the one I've been longing to start putting miles on throughout some delays this year. Let's go! #Mercedes #AMG #GTBlackSeries #Shmeemobile #Shmee150

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Tim - Shmee on July 16, 2021 tagging @ferrari, @hrowenferrari, @shmee150wastaken, and @ferrariuk. May be an image of car and text that says 'ferrari.com'.

node.text: Checking out the new @ferrari 296 GTB! They've managed to give it 830hp from the new 3l TT V6 with an electric motor, all to the rear wheels, while adding the latest tech from the curved screen to touch control steering wheel. Visually there are clues from numerous other Ferrari models, and this car also wears the Assetto Fiorano with a track focused set of shock absorbers, more carbon fibre, lexan rear glass and more, plus the optional painted livery. Like the older Dino models, the name comes from the 2.992cc V6 and Gran Turismo Berlinetta #Ferrari #296GTB #AssettoFiorano #firstlook #Shmee150

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Tim - Shmee on July 15, 2021 tagging @astonmartinlagonda, and @shmee150wastaken. May be an image of 1 person and car.

node.text: The new @astonmartinlagonda Valhalla! Now with a 4.0l twin turbo V8 and two electric motors for a total hybrid output of 950hp. The supercar will go into production in 2023, with a design that has been reworked from the original concept, and it sits in the line beneath Valkyrie but above the future mid-engine sports car that will be the Vanquish. No question, it looks incredible! #AstonMartin #Valhalla #firstlook #Shmee150
